</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph blockId="8.[113,646,1483,1604]" pageId="8" pageNumber="79">
northern 
<collectingCountry box="[221,351,1483,1509]" name="Madagascar" pageId="8" pageNumber="79">Madagascar</collectingCountry>
from 
<quantity box="[423,538,1483,1509]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.25" metricValueMax="8.5" metricValueMin="0.0" pageId="8" pageNumber="79" unit="m" value="42.5" valueMax="85.0" valueMin="0.0">0 to 85 m</quantity>
elevation (Fig. 9). The species has been recorded in flower from February to April and in fruit in May, July to August, and October through November.
</paragraph>
